assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Soltec Power Holdings, S.A. engages in the development of integrated solutions for photovoltaic energy projects in Spain, Italy, Brazil, the United States, Mexico, Argentina, Chile, Colombia, Panama, Peru, Australia, China, India, Thailand, France, Denmark, Egypt, Israel, and Kenya. The company engages in the design, manufacturing, installation, and marketing of photovoltaic solar trackers; development of installation projects for the production of photovoltaic solar electricity through the sale, transmission, and/or acquisition; and marketing and management of renewable energy equipment based on supply, installation, and maintenance works. It is also involved in the provision of technical engineering services and activities related to technical advice; production and sale of renewable energies; construction, installation, repair, and maintenance of facilities related to renewable energies; development services office; management of solar and photovoltaic projects; supervision of electrical contraction works; and exploitation and implementation of solar energy. The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Murcia, Spain.
